title: Hitachi HNAS: Storage Pools
agents: hitachi_hnas_rest
catalog: hw/storagehw/hitachi
license: GPLv2
distribution: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH
description:
 This check monitors the storage pools (spans) of a Hitachi NAS
 (HNAS) system via the File Storage REST API. It requires the
 special agent "Hitachi HNAS via REST API" to be configured for
 the host.

 The check reports the space usage of each storage pool and alerts
 if the configurable levels (default: 80%/90%) are exceeded. If the
 storage pool reports itself as not healthy, the service goes CRIT.

item:
 The label of the storage pool.

discovery:
 One service is created for each storage pool.
